docs.text: IMP01  Project documentation with Markdown. IMAP01 ia a support solution for designing maintenance plans, programs and actions that, based on AI, provides timely and reliable info on the engineering-system status. Start by reading the introductory tutorial , then check the User Guide for more information. Getting Started User Guide Features Data Cleaning & Labeling There's a stack of very important functionalities available for cleaning and labeling your data. Choose between upload a: dataset and report . Feature Engeniering & Visualization There's a stack of very important functionalities available for choosing and visuzalize your data. Choose between: extracting parameters , ... Training & Testing There's a stack of very important functionalities available for training and testing your models. Choose between: supervised , autoencoders , ... Evaluation There's a stack of very important functionalities available for evaluating the status of your equipments. Choose between: real-time and offline evaluations
